sub_title: Head of Sales/ Tech/ B2B/ B2C/International
summary:
I am currently exploring new opportunities as head of commercial, sales, international expansion. 

A third culture kid who grew up in Luxembourg to French and German parents, I quickly found a place professionally building bridges between cultures, fitting needs with wants and creating wants for needs. I'm inspired and motivated by organisations that move in new and growing spaces: tech, and social impact. I'm an innovative thinker and an asset to my teams because I know that everyone from the CEO to the intern has something to teach me, and I'm willing to learn it. 

My extensive European network across verticals means that I am a true team player and excellent communicator. My thought leadership skills have brought me to manage various teams in Europe remotely and onsite. I speak 6 languages fluently and have lived across Europe and South America. 

Mission-driven enterprises resonate the most, especially future of food, of future of mobility and future of work. 

I have developed a passion for diversity and inclusion while working as Co-Chair of the Gender Network for the British government as well as for the foodtech industry as I worked for a French Michelin Star restaurant during my sabbatical.
